title: BARD - Not With a Blame Game
itunes:title: BARD - Not With a Blame Game
description:
Mark and Gary continue the Sunday tradition as they get together Sunday morning to cover a somewhat insane video from CNN's Jake Tapper as well as a story that has rocked the chess world to its very core. 

Watch Beyond A Reasonable Doubt on YouTube at YouTube.com/ReasonableDoubtPodcast and subscribe while you're there.
